.env.example

# reCAPTCHA secret key (server)
RECAPTCHA_SECRET=

# SMTP settings for sending contact emails
SMTP_HOST=
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_SECURE=false
SMTP_USER=
SMTP_PASS=
SUPPORT_EMAIL=info@dookan.af

# WhatsApp admin number (optional)
WHATSAPP_ADMIN_NUMBER=

# Example / notes:
# - Use a provider like Mailtrap, SendGrid, or your SMTP server.
# - For Mailtrap, set `SMTP_HOST=smtp.mailtrap.io`, `SMTP_PORT=2525`, and
#   put your Mailtrap credentials into `SMTP_USER` and `SMTP_PASS`.
# - Set `SUPPORT_EMAIL` to the destination inbox for contact submissions.
